snippet.title: [Part 1/2] Tribute to Video Game Music (2 Years Anniversary!)
snippet.description:
Wow, we're now at 2 years. This is absolutely crazy. The reason I've gone this far is all thanks to you guys and your support. When I first started and uploaded that Wild Arms song, I really thought it would go nowhere. Video game music wasn't really popular on youtube at that time. I'm extremely glad I was wrong.

Thanks for the support and the subscriptions. Keep the comments and ratings coming, we've developed a nice community!

Make sure to check out Part 2: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XBp7LEnHyHo

1 Year Anniversary : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aKjpJUtbAsM
3 Years Anniversary : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RpdJnC2u84
4 Years Anniversary : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uq4ifSc7MSw
